                     <interp inst="t17861025-118-off645" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17861025-118-off645" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17861025-118-cd646" type="crimeDate">22d day of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861025-118-off645 t17861025-118-cd646"></join> last, one wooden boat, called a wherry, value 39 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17861025-118-victim1419" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Crutchfield
                  <interp inst="t17861025-118-victim1419" type="surname" value="Crutchfield"></interp>
